Dashboard Design

Healthcare Dashboard

Designed an intuitive dashboard for healthcare professionals to manage patient data and improve workflow efficiency.

Figma Design Systems Accessibility Healthcare UX
{/* Project Image */}
{/* Project Details */}
{/* Left Column */}

Project Overview

This healthcare dashboard project was designed for a large hospital network looking to modernize their patient management system. The existing system was fragmented across multiple applications, causing inefficiencies and potential errors in patient care.

The goal was to create a unified, intuitive dashboard that would streamline workflows for doctors, nurses, and administrative staff while maintaining the highest standards of data security and accessibility compliance.

The new dashboard improved workflow efficiency by 50% and reduced the time healthcare professionals spent on administrative tasks, allowing them to focus more on patient care.

{/* Right Column */}

Key Achievements

50% Workflow Efficiency Improvement

Streamlined processes reduced time spent on administrative tasks.

Enhanced Data Security

Implemented role-based access controls and audit trails for HIPAA compliance.

Improved Patient Outcomes

Better data visibility led to more informed clinical decisions and faster response times.
{/* Process Section */}

Design Process

1

Stakeholder Research

Conducted interviews with doctors, nurses, and administrators to understand their workflows, pain points, and requirements.

2

Design & Validation

Created wireframes and prototypes, conducted usability testing with healthcare professionals, and iterated based on feedback.

3

Implementation & Training

Collaborated with development team, ensured accessibility compliance, and provided comprehensive training for end users.

{/* Key Features */}

Key Features

Patient Overview Dashboard

Centralized view of patient information including vital signs, medications, test results, and care plans, with real-time updates and alerts for critical changes.

Role-Based Access Control

Customized interfaces for different user roles (doctors, nurses, administrators) with appropriate data access levels and HIPAA-compliant security measures.

Mobile Responsive Design

Optimized for tablet and mobile use, allowing healthcare professionals to access patient information and update records from anywhere in the facility.

Analytics & Reporting

Built-in analytics tools for tracking patient outcomes, identifying trends, and generating reports for quality improvement initiatives.

{/* Accessibility & Compliance */}

Accessibility & Compliance

WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance

Ensured the dashboard meets accessibility standards with proper color contrast, keyboard navigation, screen reader support, and alternative text for all images.

HIPAA Security

Implemented comprehensive security measures including encryption, audit trails, automatic session timeouts, and secure authentication protocols.

{/* Results & Impact */}
